### ==========================================
### REPLYAI - Payment API Testing
### ==========================================
### Gunakan dengan VS Code REST Client extension
### atau copy ke Postman/Insomnia
### ==========================================

### Variables (update sesuai environment)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@adminEmail = admin@example.com
@adminPassword = password
@userEmail = user@example.com
@userPassword = password

### ==========================================
### 1. AUTHENTICATION
### ==========================================

### Login sebagai User
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email={{userEmail}}&password={{userPassword}}

### Login sebagai Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email={{adminEmail}}&password={{adminPassword}}

### ==========================================
### 2. CHECKOUT FLOW
### ==========================================

### Get Pricing Page
GET {{baseUrl}}/pricing

### Get Checkout Page (Plan Pro)
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkout/pro

### Process Checkout - Monthly
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout/pro
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

duration=1&promo_code=&payment_method=manual

### Process Checkout - Yearly
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout/pro
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

duration=12&promo_code=&payment_method=manual

### ==========================================
### 3. PAYMENT API
### ==========================================

### Get Payment Detail (ganti INVOICE_NUMBER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payment/INV-2026-00001

### Apply Promo Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/payment/1/apply-promo
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

promo_code=PROMO10

### Upload Payment Proof (gunakan form-data di Postman)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payment/1/upload-proof
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="proof"; filename="proof.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-proof.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### ==========================================
### 4. MIDTRANS WEBHOOK (Security Tests)
### ==========================================

### Test: Invalid Signature
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/midtrans/notification
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "order_id": "INV-2026-00001",
    "status_code": "200",
    "gross_amount": "5000000",
    "signature_key": "invalid_signature",
    "transaction_status": "settlement"
}

### Test: Valid Signature (update dengan signature yang benar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/midtrans/notification
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "order_id": "INV-2026-00001-1234567890",
    "status_code": "200",
    "gross_amount": "5000000",
    "signature_key": "CORRECT_SHA512_SIGNATURE_HERE",
    "transaction_status": "settlement",
    "transaction_id": "trx-123456",
    "payment_type": "bank_transfer"
}

### Test: Amount Mismatch
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/midtrans/notification
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "order_id": "INV-2026-00001",
    "status_code": "200",
    "gross_amount": "1000000",
    "signature_key": "SIGNATURE_FOR_1M",
    "transaction_status": "settlement"
}

### ==========================================
### 5. CHECK STATUS
### ==========================================

### Check Midtrans Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/midtrans/status/INV-2026-00001

### ==========================================
### 6. MANUAL TESTING CHECKLIST
### ==========================================

### [ ] Price Manipulation Test
### 1. Buka checkout page
### 2. Inspect element, coba ubah hidden input harga
### 3. Submit - harus tetap pakai harga database

### [ ] Multiple Payment Test  
### 1. Checkout plan Pro
### 2. Jangan bayar, buat checkout lagi plan Pro yang sama
### 3. Harus redirect ke invoice yang sama, bukan buat baru

### [ ] Expired Payment Test
### 1. Set expires_at payment ke masa lalu via database
### 2. Jalankan: php artisan payments:cleanup-expired
### 3. Status harus berubah jadi 'failed'

### [ ] Midtrans Callback Test
### 1. Akses /checkout/midtrans/finish dengan parameter palsu
### 2. Harus check ke Midtrans API dulu
### 3. Tidak langsung mark as paid
